<i>adverb</i>: 존중히 [존중히], 삼가 [삼가], 깍듯이 [깍뜨시], 공경히 [공경히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>존중히 [존중히]</dt><br>
<dd>respectfully</dd><br>
<dd>의견이나 사람을 높이어 귀중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of thinking highly of and valuing an opinion or person.</dd><br>
<dt>삼가 [삼가]</dt><br>
<dd>respectfully; courteously; humbly</dd><br>
<dd>조심스럽고 정중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a cautious and polite manner.</dd><br>
<dt>깍듯이 [깍뜨시]</dt><br>
<dd>courteously; respectfully</dd><br>
<dd>매우 예의가 바르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very politely.</dd><br>
<dt>공경히 [공경히]</dt><br>
<dd>respectfully; reverently</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람을 공손히 받들어 모시는 마음으로.</dd><br>
<dd>With respect for the elderly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>